            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]重要！#暴雨灾后的健康提示#】①不食用被雨水浸泡过的食物，特别是变质、霉变的食物；②不接触或食用不明原因死亡的动物及阴雨水后出现的菌类；③不赤足...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>重要！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E7%81%BE%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E7%81%BE%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#暴雨灾后的健康提示#</span></a>】①不食用被雨水浸泡过的食物，特别是变质、霉变的食物；②不接触或食用不明原因死亡的动物及阴雨水后出现的菌类；③不赤足蹚水；④不饮用生水；⑤皮肤在雨天浸泡了，要及时洗热水澡清洗，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E6%B5%B8%E6%B3%A1%E5%90%8E%E8%A6%81%E6%B7%8B%E6%B5%B4%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A1%E6%BE%A1%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E6%B5%B8%E6%B3%A1%E5%90%8E%E8%A6%81%E6%B7%8B%E6%B5%B4%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A1%E6%BE%A1%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#暴雨天皮肤浸泡后要淋浴不要泡澡#</span></a>👇🏻阿卫提醒：灾害后的卫生防疫别大意！ <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4930224337387541" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1hgi5k7t4lhj60k00zkdhd02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/hriGcxIdlx087u4s2NWg01041200kGxW0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691097168&amp;ssig=5K5J5cRPyX&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/HR3sOf7Mlx087u4rubzW01041200bFz70E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691097168&amp;ssig=3nsIljmV0t&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/UgtnH7cRlx087u4qXFOo010412006l6r0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691097168&amp;ssig=ev1iu9oEEr&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4930224337387541&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
